      "text": [
        " «إِذَا كَبَّرَ وَ أَقَامَ صُلْبَهُ ثُمَّ رَكَعَ فَقَدْ أَدْرَكَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1151 - Abu Usamah narrated that he asked about a man who reaches the Imam while he is in the bowing position (ruku').\nImam (as) said: \"If he pronounces the takbir and straightens his back (stands up properly) and then bows, he has caught the rak'ah.\""
        ]
      }
